MediaKit
========

:Maintainer: David Chisnall
:Authors: David Chisnall
:License: Modified BSD License
:Version: 0.1

This is a work-in-progress replacement for MultimediaKit.  It currently only 
plays music files. It uses OSS for sound output and libavcodec / libavformat for 
file parsing.

To know more about MediaKit: 
<http://www.etoile-project.org/dev/0.4/MediaKit>


Build and Install
-----------------

Read INSTALL document.


Mac OS X support
----------------

MediaKit isn't supported on Mac OS X and there is no plan to do so. 
